{
  "stem": "9601.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The first one to go was my father because we lived closest to the inn.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We lived like five houses away from the inn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father used tell me-- he didn't tell me directly, but when he used to talk with other men, because I didn't have enough sense so ask my father how-- what happened.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was the first one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He knew all those guys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, they got him in the middle, and they were going to beat the hell out of him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he started hollering, boys!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What the hell are you guys doing?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, I-- Well, they became embarrassed because they used to come in mooch candies from him, you know, come to the store-- steal from their mother an egg to buy some candy, and you never turned them into their parents.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, what you going-- He probably understood people better than I ever will.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he says, he got away the easiest, because they open up the trap door into the cellar, and the cellar steps were all the bricks-- you know the sharp corners-- he said he got away easy.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Can you imagine what the other men?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they called in-- the-- you know, the more men came in the vicious-- the more vicious they became.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in the morning, the cellar had an outside little trap like a chute, because they used to chute the potatoes there and the sugar beets.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So if you were lucky and you got to that little opening, which was right next to the door that got into the room.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The room was ground level and the chute was right below the door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they got everybody in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
